reviewText: Low budget, not funny, ghetto as heII, inane, inept, cheap, stupid, pointless, low class..and Todd Bridges .... and wishes it had an ounce of style, substance or even budget that any of the Friday films had..  There, 20 words... AVOID .. unless you're the type who washes your floors with raw bleach and keeps your dvd's in a stack on a living room speaker, but always wonders "I wonder why my  movies be freezin' up??", then this this film is definitely for you..

And I thought the obese actor who went around the set with an open umbrella, even going to the bathroom with it,--was lame.  Overall.though, I give the movie six stars and thumb-ups!!!!!!

The current rating of 2.5 is way to generous. If you don't mind wasting over an hour of your life to a movie that could be filmed better on a i-phone then go for it.
Pros: If you know who Todd Bridges is then this is the only pro for the entire movie is his 80's star power name..
Cons: *Terrible Acting *Everything is way overacted *Music score is terrible and for being in the bay area there is way more musicians/rappers they could have got to make this movie gel and actually work better *Director is Terrible as the film had no direction or vision and it just "bumbled" all the way through to the end *Some reviews have said if you like the Friday movie Franchise you will like this movie: UH...No You won't as this is pure garbage *Some reviews say that if you like Cheech And Chong movies you will like this...NO, you won't and the only similarity is both movies had weed in it other than that this is the worst acted worst produced piece of garbage of a movie that looks so dated. * Pretty much this cannot be compared to any other movies as this one is pure and utter garbage! So embarrassed for all of the bay area for this movie as this one is ridiculous! This maybe funny if your a three year old because you won't understand what the heck these guys are saying!
If you value your time at all stay away! Support and watch another independent flick that is actually decent. This movie quite honestly deserves 0 stars! If you paid a cent for this movie you paid too much and hopefully you can get a refund on your money
